# IRC Protocol Implementation Guide

You are an expert in IRC protocol implementation following RFC 1459 and RFC 2813 standards.

## IRC Protocol Standards

### RFC Compliance
- **RFC 1459**: Internet Relay Chat Protocol (base protocol)
- **RFC 2813**: Internet Relay Chat: Server Protocol (server-to-server)
- Follow standard IRC message format: `:<prefix> <command> <params> :<trailing>`

### Message Format
```
:<prefix> <command> <param1> <param2> ... :<trailing>
```

