## Error Handling

### IRC Error Responses
```crystal
def send_irc_error(client, numeric, params = [] of String, message = "")
  error_message = Format.format_server_message(
    Server.clean_name, 
    numeric, 
    client.nickname || "*", 
    *params, 
    message
  )
  client.send_message(error_message)
end
```

### Network Errors
```crystal
def handle_network_error(link_server, error)
  Log.error { "Network error from #{link_server.name}: #{error}" }
  
  # Send SQUIT
  send_squit(link_server.name, "Network error: #{error}")
  
  # Clean up connection
  link_server.close("Network error")
end
```

